               <p>WILLIAM HOLLAND. On the 19th of March I went to <placeName id="t18300415-363-crimeloc1965">Smithfield</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18300415-363-crimeloc1965" type="placeName" value="Smithfield"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18300415-363-crimeloc1965" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300415-363-off1963 t18300415-363-crimeloc1965"></join> to select a horse, and while trying him in a cart I was pushed about, and felt a pull at my pocket - I put my hand, and missed my handkerchief, which I had safe five minutes before; it was then half-past three o'clock in the afternoon - the prisoner was going towards the pens- I followed, and took him; he was doubling up this handkerchief, which is mine.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18300415-363-person2993">
                  THOMAS 
                  BROWN
               <interp inst="t18300415-363-person2993" type="surname" value="BROWN"></interp>
