                     <interp inst="t18300415-363-person2993" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I saw the prisoner take the handkerchief from the prosecutor on the 19th of March - he rolled it under his apron, walked away, and the prosecutor took him with it.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. It was ten minutes before they took me.</p>
               <p>MR. HOLLAND. I took him directly they came to rescue him - one man said he was an officer, but I would not let him go.</p>
